(154, 1, '2021-08-19 09:45:50', '2021-08-19 09:45:50', '<strong style=\"color: #990000\">What can you achieve using Email Subscribers?</strong><p>Add subscription forms on website, send HTML newsletters. You can also Import or Export subscribers from any list to Email Subscribers.</p> <strong style=\"color: #990000\">Plugin Features</strong><ol> <li>Send notification emails to subscribers when new blog posts are published.</li> <li>Subscribe form available with 3 options to setup.</li> <li>Double Opt-In and Single Opt-In support.</li> <li>Email notification to admin when a new user signs up (Optional).</li> <li>Automatic welcome email to subscriber.</li> <li>Auto add unsubscribe link in the email.</li> <li>Import/Export subscriber emails to migrate to any lists.</li> <li>Default WordPress editor to create emails.</li> </ol> <strong>Thanks & Regards,</strong><br/>Admin<br/>', 'Welcome To Email Subscribers', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'welcome-to-email-subscribers', '', '', '2021-08-19 09:45:50', '2021-08-19 09:45:50', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/es_template/welcome-to-email-subscribers/', 0, 'es_template', '', 0),
